reviews.text: Food good quality. Authentic tastes. Excellent value for money. My favorite restaurant in the area!
Big portion. Food yummy too. Clean and comfortable environment. Worth trying.

This place is a sobering reminder of “being different doesn’t mean being better”! I visited at 3pm and not everything in the menu was available! There was only one condiment in each bowl and customers were allowed to add more but at a ridiculously exorbitant price! I ordered a hot-and-sour beef one and here was the verdict: the so-called “hot and sour” taste was so underwhelming, the noodles were over-boiled and almost turned into a shapeless mush, the beef tasted like cardboard, the whole bowl was just lukewarm! This place was just TOTALLY UNACCEPTABLE!
OK
乾淨，服務可以。米線好味，值得來吃

reviews.text: 乾淨，服務可以。米線好味，值得來吃
健康的一餐，氣鍋雞沒有加多餘的調味料。附近沒有同類的食肆，值得一試。
米線好正，同其它店舖的唔同，因是自家新鮮制造，D菌是由老板親自到雲南選購運回港，是正宗雲南口味，而嗰杯金茶皇奶茶一個字( 正)，大家入開粉嶺一定要去試試。
Food good quality. Authentic tastes. Excellent value for money. My favorite restaurant in the area!
環境一般。食物中上
